OL,4,CTwitter tells users to be nice and
OL,5,Cthink twice before replying
OL,6, Twitter will now prompt users to review
OL,7, and revise "potentially harmful or
OL,8, offensive" replies.
OL,10,FThe social media platform, which has
OL,11,Foften faced criticism over abusive user
OL,12,Fbehaviour, tested the feature last
OL,13,Fyear.
OL,15,FTwitter said the tests showed that the
OL,16,Fprompts reduced offensive replies.
OL,18,FOn Wednesday, the company said it would
OL,19,Froll the prompts out to English
OL,20,Flanguage accounts using Twitter on
OL,21,FApple and Android.
